that students very much appreciate having access to those cheat sheets and help resources all within

00:58:05.199 --> 00:58:09.360
the cloud. So I think you'll find it, you know, for those faculty who want to just kind of experiment

00:58:09.360 --> 00:58:15.760
with it, I think you'll find it fairly accessible. Absolutely. Thanks for pointing that out. The

00:58:15.760 --> 00:58:21.120
cheat sheets are super popular. Down to the last minute, it looks like we have one last question

